&lt;p&gt;The Accounts Receivable Applet manages all customer billing, payment processing, and collections activities in BigLedger&amp;rsquo;s Accounting Module, providing comprehensive receivables management and customer credit control.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Primary Functions&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;primary-functions&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#primary-functions&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Invoicing&lt;/strong&gt; - Invoice generation and delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payment Processing&lt;/strong&gt; - Customer payment recording and matching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collections Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Overdue account management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Credit Control&lt;/strong&gt; - Customer credit limits and monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aging Analysis&lt;/strong&gt; - Receivables aging and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Features&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;key-features&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#key-features&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;TODO: Expand Key Features Section&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;todo-expand-key-features-section&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
