&lt;li&gt;Automated invoice generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple payment method support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer statement generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Credit limit monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collection workflow automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
